### visitSymbolBegin() {#ad0a0e3e3c9a99f6401aeeeae595f654f}

<MemberDefinition

Paired begin/end actions for all symbols.

Receives all record data, including the fixed-length record prefix. <a href="#ad0a0e3e3c9a99f6401aeeeae595f654f">visitSymbolBegin()</a> should return the type of the Symbol, or an error if it cannot be determined.
